2000-10-10  Von Welch  <vwelch@ncsa.uiuc.edu>

	* gsi_socket.c, gsi_socket_test.c, myproxy.c, myproxy_creds.c,
	myproxy_server.c, myproxy_server_config.c: Replaced snprintf()
	calles with functions from string_func.c because of snprintf()
	being non-existant on Solaris 2.5.1 boxes and behavioral
	differences in return value between gnu libc and solaris
	implementations.

	* myproxy.c: Added encode_command(), encode_response() and
	encode_lifetime() functions.
	
	* myproxy_log.c: Removed my_vsnprintf() as it is now in
	string_funcs.c

	* verror.c: Removed my_vsnprintf() as it is now in
	string_funcs.c
	
	* string_funcs.c, string_funcs.h: Created these files.

	* myproxy_destroy.c (main): Bug fix - use created proxy file for
	authentication and not default proxy.
	(main): Bug fix - passphrase was not being correctly read.

2000-10-09  Von Welch  <vwelch@ncsa.uiuc.edu>

	* verror.c (my_vsnprintf): Fixed inverted logic in checking of
	HAVE_VSNPRINTF
	
2000-10-04  Von Welch  <vwelch@ncsa.uiuc.edu>

	* myproxy_server.c (main): Print strerror() when failure occurs
	opening configuration file.

	* myproxy.c(parse_command): Fixed command_value type.

2000-10-03  Von Welch  <vwelch@ncsa.uiuc.edu>

	* ssl_utils.c: Fixes for openssl build with PEM callback
	differences (openssl has a user data parameter while ssleay does
	not).

	* ChangeLog: Created after 0.2alpha1 release

